newsitem.title: USA: Franklin Cty SDFC, Ky., won by Morgan Keegan.
newsitem.headline: Franklin Cty SDFC, Ky., won by Morgan Keegan.

text.p: Morgan Keegan said it won $4.250 million of Franklin Cty. SDFC, Ky., school building refunding revenue bonds, Series 1996 with a net interest cost of 4.84 percent.
